## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-102">這`enum`引發事件時指定的事件類型<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-102">This `enum` specifies the event type when an event is raised for an <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-103">修改 XML 樹狀結構的所有作業都細分為一連串的基本項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-103">All operations that modify the XML tree break down to a series of primitives.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-104">有四種類型的基本項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-104">There are four types of primitives.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-105">兩個基本項目 （Add 和 Remove） 處理的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-105">Two of the primitives (Add and Remove) act on collections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-106">兩個 （名稱和值） 處理執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-106">Two of them (Name and Value) act on instances.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-107">沒有下列基本類型的每個相對應的事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-107">There is a corresponding event for each of these primitives.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-108">修改 XML 樹狀結構內其中一個事件，因為這樣可能會導致非預期的結果時，您應該要小心。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-108">You should be careful when modifying an XML tree within one of these events, because doing this might lead to unexpected results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-109">例如，如果您收到<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changing>事件，並在處理事件時的樹狀結構中移除節點，您可能不會收到<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changed>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-109">For example, if you receive a <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changing> event, and while the event is being processed you remove the node from the tree, you might not receive the <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changed> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-110">處理事件時，它是有效修改 XML 樹狀結構不是包含節點所收到的事件，若要修改相同的樹狀結構中，提供所做的修改不會影響在其引發事件的特定節點更正確。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-110">When an event is being processed, it is valid to modify an XML tree other than the one that contains the node that is receiving the event; it is even valid to modify the same tree provided the modifications do not affect the specific nodes on which the event was raised.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-111">不過，如果您修改包含收到事件的節點的樹狀目錄的區域，您會收到的事件和影響樹狀結構會定義。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-111">However, if you modify the area of the tree that contains the node receiving the event, the events that you receive and the impact to the tree are undefined.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-112">下列範例會藉由將樹狀結構中的項目引發事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-112">The following example raises an event by adding an element to the tree.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root", "content");  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Add(new XElement("Child", "child content"));  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-113">這個範例會產生下列輸出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-113">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changing: Add  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changed: Add  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-114">下列範例會藉由從樹狀結構移除項目引發事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-114">The following example raises an event by removing an element from the tree.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root",  
    new XElement("Child", "content")  
);  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Element("Child").Remove();  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-115">這個範例會產生下列輸出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-115">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changing: Remove  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changed: Remove  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-116">下列範例會引發事件，藉由變更項目的名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-116">The following example raises an event by changing the name of an element.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root", "content");  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Name = "NewName";  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-117">這個範例會產生下列輸出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-117">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changing: Name  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changed: Name  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-118">下列範例會引發事件，藉由設定屬性的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-118">The following example raises an event by setting the value of an attribute.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root",  
    new XAttribute("Att", "att value")  
);  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.FirstAttribute.Value = "new contents";  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="afcdb-119">這個範例會產生下列輸出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="afcdb-119">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XAttribute  
  Changing: Value  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XAttribute  
  Changed: Value  
```
